{
  "texts": [
    "Yang et al.",
    "15 employed GPT-based and diffusion-based generative AI models to design novel polymer electrolytes with enhanced ionic conductivity, demonstrating significant improvements in generative model performance.",
    "However, the application of these generative models in the field of battery research is still in the preliminary stage, which requires more investigations.",
    "Through supervised learning, we can predict future data points based on previously labeled data (X, y).",
    "Supervised learning mainly includes regression and classification tasks and can be accomplished by various ML algorithms, such as linear regression (LR), support vector machines (SVM), random forests (RF), K nearest neighbors (KNN), extreme gradient boosting (XGB) and artificial neural network (ANN)."
  ]
}